  "body": "Hey Guys Im having the following problem/question:\nIm using a PoA private network with a blocktime of 0. I can broadcast transactions and they are mined as they should.\nIf I send a transaction with gasPrice too low, all the miners ignore this transaction. That's OK for me but then all future transactions from this account get ignored by miners even if they have the correct gasPrice.\nWhat is wrong here? Thx for helping.",
