    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Transactions are ordered by an increasing number called nonce. If a transaction gets dropped (e.g. by specifying to little gas) all following transactions are stuck until a transaction is mined with the same nonce as the transaction that was dropped. So to unstuck all transactions you need to re-submit a transaction with the correct nonce.\r\n",
